*** Variables ***
${OKTA_USER}        your.email@company.com
${OKTA_PASSWORD}    your_password

*** Test Cases ***
Login Through Okta SSO
    Click Element    xpath=//a[contains(., 'Single Sign-On')] | //button[contains(., 'Single Sign-On')]


    Wait Until Page Contains Element    xpath=(//input[@type='email' or @type='text'])[1]


    Input Text    xpath=(//input[@type='email' or @type='text'])[1]    ${OKTA_USER}

    Click Button    xpath=//input[@type='submit' or contains(@value, 'Next') or contains(@value, 'Continue')] | //button[contains(., 'Next') or contains(., 'Continue')]

    Wait Until Page Contains Element    xpath=//input[@type='password']

    Input Text    xpath=//input[@type='password']    ${OKTA_PASSWORD}


    Click Button    xpath=//input[@type='submit' or contains(@value, 'Verify') or contains(@value, 'Sign In')] | //button[contains(., 'Verify') or contains(., 'Sign In')]


    Wait Until Page Contains    Dashboard

